# SignalR-Chat.Mobile
A real-time chat application for Android
![](https://github.com/AKouki/SignalR-Chat/blob/master/Chat.Web/Content/screenshots/android.png)

## Getting Started
To run this application you need to download and run Chat.Web

### Dependencies
* [SignalR Android Client](https://github.com/SignalR/java-client)
* Gson
* HttpClient
`android {
    useLibrary 'org.apache.http.legacy'
}`

